# Burn & Build — one repo

Repo: **`pwa-burn-and-build`** (this workspace)

| Path | Host | Role |
|------|------|------|
| `landing/` | gettheburnandbuildapp.com (GitHub Pages) | Marketing — hero, calculator, testimonials, $149 CTA |
| `createyourfoodplan/` | Render `/createyourfoodplan/` | Program creator — email → intake → Stripe → save plan |
| `shell/` | GitHub Pages or Render `/shell/` | Daily app — food plan, grocery, logging |
| `server/` | Render | API + SQLite for programs/contacts |

**Flow:** Landing CTA → Render creator → shell app.

**Deploy landing:** push to `main` (changes under `landing/`) → GitHub Actions workflow `deploy-landing.yml`. In repo **Settings → Pages**, source must be **GitHub Actions** (not the old `burnandbuildlandingpage` repo).

**Not connected to Hardkor Diet** or **Signal+** (separate products).
